ISLAMABAD, Jan 20 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Thursday expressed deep  and sorrow over loss of precious human lives in the Lahore blast.
The minister extended his condolences to the families of those killed in the blast and prayed for speedy recovery of the injured.
